    "body": "Fixes #8772\r\n\r\nWhen chaining Spack installations, the upstream Spack instance is **not** supposed to be locked; however, that is not currently the case. \r\n\r\nThis PR ensures the `ForbiddenLock` is retained for upstream databases and associated operations do not attempt to acquire read locks.\r\n\r\nTODO:\r\n- [ ]  Resolve test failure issues",
